title: Cipha Sounds: Bronx Kid
description:
Kippy and Foley are back with Cipha Sounds for a HOT ep! They talk growing up in the bronx, working in Hip Hop, and trying to buy a house with cash! Its a fun one, thanks for listening. 


Live Shows: https://linktr.ee/AYGLiveShows

Follow Kevin: https://www.instagram.com/kevinryancomedy/ 


Follow Foley: https://www.instagram.com/foleygrams/ 


Comedians H. Foley and Kevin Ryan are self proclaimed GARBAGE.


Each week a new stand up comedian gets put to the test. Steal shampoo from hotels? Own a George Foreman Grill? Ever worn JNCO Jeans?
